*Kojeg* god knjigu poželite da čitate, ja ću vam je dati. (Whichever book you want to read, I will give it to you.)

Ona je slušala razmišljanja *kojega* je bio preplavio strah. (She was listening to the thoughts which were overwhelmed by fear.)

*Kojeg* si puta preletio avionom? (How many times have you flown by plane?)

Moj brat je tražio posao *kojeg* je završio. (My brother was looking for the job he had finished.)

Ona je mislila o čoveku *kojeg* je volela. (She was thinking about the man she loved.)